$ Excel helpers

→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/helpers/highlightRow[Highlighting rows]

→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/helpers/insertComment[Inserting a comment] on the selected cell.

→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/helpers/delete-rows-meeting-criteria[Delete rows meeting an arbitrary criteria]

sa:
  Such helper functions might be stored in the → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Excel/XLSTART/Personal_xlsb[`Personal.xlsb`] Excel workbook.

  → development/languages/VBA/modules/Excel/ExcelHelpers[ExcelHelpers.bas]
